16
00:00:37,284 --> 00:00:44,048
[SPEAKER_00]: 23-328, to honorable president and members of the city of Medford City Council regarding food truck permitting.

17
00:00:44,529 --> 00:00:52,734
[SPEAKER_00]: Dear President Morrell and members of the city council, on behalf of the below entities, I respectfully submit to the Medford City Council the following request for a food truck permit in the city of Medford.

18
00:00:52,854 --> 00:00:57,017
[SPEAKER_00]: In addition to the city council approval, vendors are required to adhere to health department safety requirements.

19
00:00:57,697 --> 00:01:04,869
[SPEAKER_00]: We have entity chicken and rice guys food truck 617 12 noon to 8pm Medford Square for circle the square.

20
00:01:06,291 --> 00:01:11,941
[SPEAKER_00]: We have frozen hoagies 617 12 noon to 8pm Medford Square for circle the square.

21
00:01:12,752 --> 00:01:16,613
[SPEAKER_00]: And then we have entity frozen hoagies, 624, 10 to 6 p.m.

22
00:01:16,753 --> 00:01:18,714
[SPEAKER_00]: Duggar Park for West Medford Open Studios.

23
00:01:19,594 --> 00:01:23,316
[SPEAKER_00]: And entity bond made foods LLC, 624, 10 to 6 p.m.

24
00:01:23,356 --> 00:01:25,697
[SPEAKER_00]: Duggar Park for West Medford Open Studios.

25
00:01:26,257 --> 00:01:27,617
[SPEAKER_00]: Thank you for your kind attention to this matter.

26
00:01:27,697 --> 00:01:29,898
[SPEAKER_00]: Sincerely yours, Brianna Lungo Kern, Mayor.

27
